Lakshmi

00:05:10.200 --> 00:05:11.440
memberi saya banyak uang.

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:15.760
Kata-katanya menyakiti
perasaanku, Ayush!

00:05:17.360 --> 00:05:18.320
Hatiku...

