Ayah,

00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:04.960
nenek, ibu,

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:06.560
tante...

00:10:08.040 --> 00:10:09.400
Semua orang pasti sedih.

00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:12.920
Aku akan mempermalukan semua orang.

00:10:15.200 --> 00:10:16.200
saya harap

00:10:17.880 --> 00:10:19.200
Lakshmi bersamaku.

